################################################################################################################################
############ A GEANT4 based framework to simulate Fractionally Charged Particles ###############################################
################################################################################################################################
The repository contains source codes to simulate passage of Fractionally Charged Particles through any typical detectot material. The "src" directory has all the files with .cc extension and the
"include" directory has the corressponding header files with .hh extension. A full apllication with a very simplified detector geometry, a GNUmakefile, the main function and a macro is given to run a
test simulation. User must define his or her own simulation geometry.

